INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2010-12-14 22:35:31', 'If you are interested in a temporary position on the crew for the 2011 season you should be contacting us soon....very, very soon. We will be requesting a referral list in January.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe referral list for the GS-0462-4/5 Senior Firefighter has been requested, however the announcement has been closed due to IFPM requirements. If you applied initially, you will receive an e-mail with instructions on how to ensure you will be on the list. If you did not apply, here is your chance to redeem yourself. The new OCR will be out on December 3rd and we will be requesting a list the first week of January.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2010-12-17 13:58:07', 'The recruiting page has been updated with the most up to date information and AVUE announcement links for the 2011 season. Please read the announcement and all associated documentation completely to ensure you apply correctly.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2010-12-13 10:00:00', 'Congratulations to Evan Hsu, the Siskiyou Rappel Crew&#039;s 2010 Rappeller of the Year.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2010-12-14 22:45:37', 'The Siskiyou Rappel Crew is now on Facebook!  The information on our &#039;Current Status&#039; page will now also be available on our Facebook page: http://www.facebook.com/pages/Siskiyou-Rappel-Crew/116587918401126?v=wall');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2010-12-15 17:59:05', 'Make sure to check out the &quot;Off-Season Prep&quot; section of our website to make sure you are ready for the 2011 season, and the &quot;Recruiting&quot; section to make sure you have a chance at a job on the crew.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-01-05 18:09:34', 'We have received the referral lists for the temporary positions and we are in the process of reviewing them. Reference checks and phone calls will take place next week, with selections to follow shortly thereafter. ');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-01-12 09:36:15', 'We have received the GS-4/5 Senior Firefighter list and are currently working through it. Depending on the schedule of management, we hope to have this finished in a couple of weeks. Stay tuned and in touch.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-01-24 20:18:56', 'We will be presenting our selection for the Senior Firefighter to the Forest Supervisor on February 10th. If you received an interview you will be contacted with the results. As always, thank you for your interest in our program.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-02-10 15:26:13', 'The selection for the Senior Firefighter position has been made and is off to ASC. Once we get the qualifications check back, the offer will be made and notifications to the individuals who received interviews will be made. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nRound 1 of the temporary hiring for the 2011 season is also complete. With some potential movement in the current roster, we may be requesting a second referral list in the weeks to come. If you still want a shot at getting on the crew, make sure that your AVUE application is up to date and you have attached all the required documentation. Call if you have questions, and good luck.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-02-17 18:52:31', 'Congratulations to Sarah Uvodich, our new GS-5 Senior Firefighter. We look forward to having her on the crew to assist in the Equipment and Operations Department starting in March.<br />\r\n');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('tlyda', '2011-02-22 09:21:34', 'Round two of the temp hiring has now begun, We maybe hiring up to 2 positions. If you are still interested make sure you have your application updated and give us a call or set up a time to stop by.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-04-01 08:05:18', 'The hiring for the 2011 crew is complete. Thanks to all who applied and were not selected, we hope to see you on the list for next season.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-04-05 14:42:57', 'Congratulations are in order to Brandon Nelson. He is officially leaving the crew to move into his new permanent position on the Umpqua NF. We are confident that he will continue to lead and train less experienced crewmembers in his new position. <br />\r\nGood job Brandon, you earned it.<br />\r\n');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2011-04-24 11:07:28', 'Happy Easter!<br />\r\nRappel Academy 1 of 5 starts tomorrow and SRC will be there.  The 2011 season is about to begin...');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2011-04-26 22:43:45', 'Training hard with rappellers from across the nation.  The first live rappels of 2011 were conducted today between snow flurries in John Day.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2011-04-30 12:07:59', 'The first national veteran recertification has been successfully completed.  Rappellers touched down into 4 inches of snow on Friday morning to finish the last of their training.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRe-cert #2 begins Monday morning with a fresh batch of rappellers and spotters...');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2011-05-06 22:26:53', 'The 2nd Veteran Rappeller Re-Certification for 2011 has been completed.  The entire veteran staff of the Siskiyou Rappel Crew is now re-certified for the coming fire season and ready to train our new crewmembers starting on Monday...');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2011-05-13 19:08:15', 'The first week of rookie training has been completed.  Everyone gave their sweat and blood for the crew this week as body and mind were tested - next week we should be able to throttle the program up to full speed.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2011-05-23 22:57:40', 'Field week complete!<br />\r\nNow it&#039;s back to the classroom for helicopter crewmember training.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-06-05 21:42:29', 'The National Rookie Rappel Academy is here. We look forward to seeing the rookies continue the tradition of hard work and perseverance throughout the week.<br />\r\nWe will also be keeping the memory of T.J. Marovich in our thoughts. Without him this national program would not have happened.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-06-13 08:11:06', 'The 2011 Rookie Rappel Academy is now over. All the SRC rookies successfully navigated their way through the program and came out the other side as academy graduates. <br />\r\nNow we wait to see when they can put their new found skills to use in the real world.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2011-06-23 20:44:55', 'We currently have crewmembers scattered around the country: Nick &amp; Cole are in AZ helping out with the Wallow Fire, Sarah is in New Mexico with the Malheur module and Tim is in Georgia on the Okefenokee.  The rest of the crew is at home on the Rogue-Siskiyou, staffing for initial attack.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-06-27 16:48:38', 'All is calm on the home front, but pretty hectic on the national scale. A few people still out on assignment, our engineer putting a fresh coat of wax on the helicopter and the rest of the crew busy with base operations and training.<br />\r\nWe wait.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-06-28 20:11:53', 'The crew and helicopter is off to New Mexico in the morning to help out on the Los Conchas fire. ');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-07-10 09:24:57', 'Helicopter and crew are currently at Lakeside Helibase in Cochiti, NM. Hot weather and active fire behavior are the norm.<br />\r\nHappy birthday goes out to our IT guy and lead crew member, Evan Hsu.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-07-15 19:59:31', 'The whole crew is back at the base and getting ready for fire season in the Pacific Northwest after a good fire assignment in NM. <br />\r\nSome belated www.HappyBirthdaywishes.com also go out to Sarah Uvodich our hairstylist and senior firefighter on the crew. ');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-08-02 10:49:53', 'Red Flag Warnings and hot temps in our coverage area, this means facilities improvements and training drills around the base. <br />\r\nCoiled springs.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-08-12 17:56:23', 'Holding pattern people.......holding pattern.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-08-13 12:44:32', 'Today is the last day for Kit Colbenson to be on the crew. Kit is moving on to the Siskiyou Mountains Ranger District of the Rogue River-Siskiyou NF to be on an engine. He has dedicated 9 years to the Siskiyou Rappel Crew, leading the way for up and coming crewmembers. <br />\r\nHis smile, calm demeanor and desire to improve the program will be missed.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-08-20 12:41:45', 'Several state fires over the last few days and lightning predicted on the forest. Fire season 2011? We will see.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-08-23 11:47:55', 'Rappellers in Crater Lake NP, boosters from Central Oregon and dry lightning predicted. ');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-09-01 15:08:23', '16 Siskiyou Rappellers are on the Nasty Fire, in the Opal Creek Wilderness on the Willamette, NF. They are being assisted by rappellers from multiple regions, which brings the grand total to 30 rappellers on the fire.<br />\r\nThey are all working hard to limit the fire growth, and we don&#039;t envy their packout.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-12-08 10:13:24', 'Congratulations are in order for Mr. and Mrs. Hsu. Evan and Mary were married on December 3rd and are currently planning their honeymoon to tropical Iceland. I for one cannot wait for the photos.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-12-08 10:18:26', 'With the weather in Southern Oregon being cold and foggy, that can only mean one thing....hiring. We will begin our 2012 temporary hiring process in January, so get your applications dusted off and into AVUE by December 31st.<br />\r\nThe links to the current OCR&#039;s are under our recruiting tab, and give us a call if you have any questions.<br />\r\nBottom line-If your name is not on the list, you won&#039;t be on the crew. Work hard and don&#039;t be left behind.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2011-10-24 15:39:52', 'The season is officially over and all of SRC&#039;s crewmembers have entered hibernation.  Preparations for 2012 are underway...');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2011-10-24 15:42:18', 'The votes are in: Congratulations to Mat Murray, the 2011 SRC Rappeller of the Year!  Well played, my friend.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-10-11 08:20:59', 'Home from John Day, the last fire of the season is in the books. The exciting life of burning, winterizing and close outs are in our future.<br />\r\nWe&#039;re not entirely done yet, but we&#039;re close.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2011-09-08 18:07:10', 'The Nasty Fire is winding down with only 4 rappellers remaining on scene to monitor.  The rest of the rappel community is staffing fires following an inexplicable storm pattern covering most of the state of Oregon.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-09-15 10:40:50', 'The crew and helicopter are currently at Toketee HB on the Umpqua, NF. A cooler weather pattern has moved us into large fire support mode, and reminded us of the importance of layering.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2011-12-16 13:33:27', 'Our GS-462-4/5 Senior Firefighter position on the crew is currently being outreached however, AVUE is in the process of revising the OCR for this position so it will not be available on the web until December 23, 2011. We will update the link on our recruiting page once this happens. The temporary GS-4 and GS-5 links are good to go.<br />\r\nIf you have any further questions on how to apply to any of these positions, call the base or drop us an e-mail and we&#039;ll get you up to speed.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-01-03 11:53:24', 'The announcement numbers for the GS-5 Senior Firefighter position have been updated on our recruiting page as of today. The temporary announcement numbers are still current and we have requested a referral list to begin round 1 of the 2012 hiring process.<br />\r\nWe are back in the office, so give us a call with any questions.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-01-24 15:27:37', 'Temporary hiring for the 2012 fire season is coming to a close. We may still have one position left to fill though, so keep in contact if your are still interested.<br />\r\nThe GS-4/5 Senior Firefighter referral list has also been requested and we should be seeing that in the next week. Interviews and reference checks will then begin.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-02-22 11:06:33', 'Due to a change in the referral list request process for 2012, we have not yet received our list. We look to have it by the end of the week though.<br />\r\nConsider yourself updated.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-03-13 14:47:33', 'We have received the list for our GS-4/5 Senior Firefighter position and the hiring team went to work on it. We have made a selection and are going down the path of approvals. We should have it to the RO by the end of the week.<br />\r\n');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-04-09 07:58:27', 'Only 6 days left for anyone interested in applying for the GS-6/7 Lead Crew detail!');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-04-23 15:41:11', 'Please welcome me in congratulating Nick Sailer as our new Senior Firefighter on the Siskiyou Rappel Crew. Nick has been a temporary seasonal on our crew since 2009 and has worked hard to advance his skills in both fire and aviation. He has held positions with the Minnesota Department of Natural Resources, the USFS at Mammoth Lakes, the Boundary Peak hand crew, the Sierra Hotshots and the Siskiyou Rappel Crew in his 11 year career. Nick&acirc;€™s great personality, strong work ethic and his desire to mentor those around him will make him an asset to the crew and the forest. He is currently attending his last training session as a temporary employee and will start in his new job May 7th. ');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2012-05-04 10:13:37', 'It all starts on Monday (5/7).  Get ready.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2012-05-21 18:48:48', 'Field Week complete.  On to helicopter crewmember class...');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2012-05-30 07:01:29', 'Week 4 of rookie training - almost there...');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-06-04 13:55:21', 'The rookies are off to Salmon Idaho to join the rest of their peers at the National Rappel Academy. Back home we are tidying up around the base, the aircraft is here and we are available nationally.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOur thoughts and prayers are with the families of the pilots in Sunday&#039;s airtanker crash in Utah.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-06-10 16:03:17', 'The helicopter and remaining crewmembers are en route to Wyoming to assist with the Guernsey Fire, while the rookies finish up rappel training in Idaho. We should all meet up in a few days to put our training to the test.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2012-06-13 16:59:52', 'The entire crew is currently assigned to the Guernsey State Park Fire in Guernsey, WY (http://inciweb.org/incident/2909/).');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-06-15 08:01:23', 'The aircraft and crew are off to Douglas, WY on a new adventure.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-06-23 09:49:41', 'The crew is currently on the Russels Camp Fire just outside Douglas, WY. We are assisting with helibase and field operations and working hard to help with containment in a critical fire weather environment at 9500&#039;. ');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2012-06-30 14:46:40', 'The crew is currently assigned to the Otter Creek Fire near Ten Sleep, Wyoming.  Sarah is managing our helicopter while Tim is assigned as the helibase manager.  The rest of the crew is engaged in structure protection along Otter Creek Canyon.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2012-07-03 07:04:57', 'The crew and helicopter are en route back to Grants Pass, Oregon after 21 days in Wyoming.  Good luck to all the crews still out there.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2012-07-08 19:36:29', 'And we&#039;re off again.  The crew is pre-positioned in La Grande for lightning.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-07-10 13:42:45', 'The crew is staffing rappel fires in NE Oregon and the helicopter is operating out of Enterprise to support them logistically. <br />\r\nHappy Birthday wishes go out to our Engineering Department lead, Evan Leward Hsu who turns 29 today. He is currently assigned to Incident 380, so if you&#039;re in the area give him a shout.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-07-11 14:29:13', 'As the work continues in NE Oregon, our equipment specialist and resident questioner Sarah Jean Uvodich is enjoying her 100th rappel and her birthday today. We hope that she is working hard and finds a little me time on the fireline.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-07-30 15:49:16', 'A few boosters to Price Valley, the rest getting reset mentally and physically in GP for the next round.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-08-01 18:06:31', 'The base is empty with the Siskiyou Rappellers and some Central Oregon boosters out on fires locally. Welcome to Dirty August.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-08-05 13:01:22', '4 boosters still at Price Valley, and the rest of us are cleaning up and getting ready for the incoming lightning. Sunny, hot and dry people.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-08-09 10:07:55', 'After a brisk round of fire activity and rappelling in the Red Buttes Wilderness, we are back . Staffing the aircraft, assisting with helibase operations on the Siskiyou N.F. and refurbing equipment for the next mission are the goings on.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe SRC boosters that went to Price Valley remain on the road and engaged in operations with that program.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-08-16 11:12:29', '4 rappellers are out in the Sky Lakes Wilderness on the Cold Springs Fire, while the rest of us are at the base getting ready for the predicted lightning.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFire weather watches for abundant lightning + dry fuels + instability= Coiled springs.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-08-18 21:14:21', 'Boosters come in, boosters go out. 8 rappellers are now out on the Rogue-Umpqua Divide Wilderness and fresh orders are on the fax machine. Umpqua here we come.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-08-21 12:47:23', 'The last few days have been very active, staffing fires and supporting fires on the Umpqua NF. Most of the crew is now at Tokotee Airstrip getting things back in order for whatever may come our way.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nToday the crew also took some time at this mornings briefing to discuss the tragedy of one of our fallen sisters, Anne Rosemarie Veseth. Our thoughts and prayers go out to the friends and family of Anne, and we hope that thay may find peace.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-09-12 11:06:42', 'The crew (minus Fabris) is at Trout Lake, WA. helping out on the Cascade Creek fire and rappelling on the Gifford Pinchot N.F.<br />\r\nNights are cold and the fire is burning actively during the day....welcome to September.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2012-09-27 21:31:56', 'Our helicopter has been extended through October 7th due to continued fire weather conditions on the forest.  The crew is ready and waiting at the Siskiyou Helibase.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-10-13 16:27:45', 'A couple of folks out on assignment and the rest of us are hanging at the base watching the never ending summer roll on. No rain out of this last storm, sunny and warm......another helicopter extension? <br />\r\nWe might end up staging at the pumpkin patch before it&#039;s all over.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2012-10-18 11:54:25', 'Fire season has officially ended in Southern Oregon.  Our helicopter left us on October 15th for another winter of heli-skiing in Canada.  The few remaining crewmembers are now cutting hazard trees and winterizing the rappel base.  Another great season has come to an end.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-12-23 22:34:48', 'Grants Pass has now been added to the temp 4 and 5 positions. We are still looking to have all the applications in by December 31st with selections to follow shortly thereafter. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nGood luck and happy holidays.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-12-27 12:44:39', 'The December 31st deadline for all temporary and permanent applications to be in is rapidly approaching. This is just a friendly reminder to have them in, have them correct and have a desire to work here.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNow back to the Holidays and your regularly scheduled programming.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-12-17 10:04:45', 'Well the jobs have all been posted on USAJobs, but as you can tell Grants Pass is not showing up on any of them. We are in contact with personnel to remedy this problem, so hang in there and get ready to hit send once we get this thing fixed.<br />\r\nThat is all.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-12-17 13:53:19', 'The Grants Pass duty station has been added to both the DEMO and MERIT announcement for the GS-6/7 Squadleader position on USAJobs. This means that we are still on track to have all the applications in by the end of December and start the hiring process in January. Just click on the recruiting tab to get the ball rolling.<br />\r\nCross your t&#039;s and dot your i&#039;s people.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2012-11-15 23:19:43', 'Falling leaves and 6 hours of foggy daylight can only mean one thing: hiring. <br />\r\nWe are currently outreaching a GS-6/7 Squad Leader permanent position on the crew with a desire to fill in the next few months. <br />\r\nWe are also fielding calls and updating our contact lists for temporary employees who want to be on the crew for the 2013 field season. <br />\r\nIf you think you have what it takes, give us a call and make sure that your USA Jobs application is up to date. Referral lists for the temporary jobs will be requested in early January.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2012-11-30 12:27:07', 'Well the votes have been counted and recounted and the results are still the same. Our friendly farmer Charles Fabris has won the honor of Siskiyou Rappel Crew&#039;s 2012 Rappeller of the Year. <br />\r\nCongratulations Charlie, you earned it.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2012-12-08 14:19:22', 'Seasonal job announcements for the 2013 fire season are now listed on the USAJobs website.  Get your applications in early - we will be pulling our applicant list at the beginning of January.  The announcement numbers are listed on our Recruiting page (http://www.siskiyourappellers.com/recruiting.php).');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-01-09 08:31:46', 'The Siskiyou Rappel Crew would like to send our condolences to the friends and family of the flight crew that was on board the Columbia Helicopter that went down in Peru on Monday.<br />\r\nThis is a tragic loss and our thoughts and prayers are with you.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-01-11 15:45:43', 'Interviews and hiring continue. We will be requesting a qualifications check on Monday the 14th to move forward with filling the 2013 roster. If you have the skills and desire to be on the crew, time is running out to put your best foot forward.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDon&#039;t be left behind.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-01-22 15:28:44', 'We have completed the temp hiring for the 2013 field season with job offers being accepted and the roster updated bringing our numbers to 21. If you did not receive an offer for this season, we appreciate your interest in our program and recommend that you keep in touch throughout the year and get your app ready for the fall.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSee you on the line.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-02-13 16:25:08', 'We have received the referral list for the GS-6/7 lead crewmember position and are actively going through all the applications. We expect to have made a selection by March 5th and to have the candidate in place by early April.<br />\r\nIf you applied for the position and wish to be considered, pick up the phone and give us a call. ');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-04-25 16:02:27', 'We are pleased to announce that we have filled 2 GS-6/7 Lead Crewmember positions on the Siskiyou Rappel Crew, and the selected individuals are in place and working hard.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nJonah Gladney comes to us from the Redmond Smokejumpers and has a strong fire background to include smokejumping and hotshots. His impressive fire experience, operational mindset and solid work ethic will make him an excellent addition to the program and the region.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBrett Ballard comes to us from the Grangeville Helitack crew and brings an energetic personality and a strong fire background as well. He has also spent time working with the Blue Mountain Rappel Crew so the transition will be a seamless process, and we look forward to his fresh ideas to keep us motivated and moving forward.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBoth of these individuals expressed a strong desire to be on this crew and work on this forest for the diversity, the  ability to affect change and to bring families closer together. Those are the foundational building blocks of this program, and the crew is excited to have them in place and doing work.<br />\r\n');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-04-29 20:01:16', 'All the vets and permanents (minus Gladney, Holloway and Taylor) are braving the elements in John Day, OR. Re-certification is the name of the game and some are moving on to live rappels tomorrow at Snow Shoe Helibase, while others get introduced to the tower and mock ups.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRookie training is in our near future.....');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-05-06 06:03:41', 'Day one of rookie training, time to walk the talk.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-05-20 10:22:53', 'Rookie week and field week are in the books with S-271 aviation training in the works this week. All the rookies are holding steady up to this point.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-06-02 08:58:12', 'Well, the rookies have all passed the Siskiyou rookie training program. The entire crew is now en route to Salmon, Idaho to get the rookies certified to rappel, help with the training and to meet up with our aircraft for the 2013 fire season.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n1 more week until game on.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-06-11 10:34:13', 'All the rookies have passed their rappel training, and the entire crew is en route home and ready to fight fire.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2013-06-13 15:03:47', 'Quinones + 8 are now assigned to the Daves Fire in California.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-06-13 18:26:24', 'The helicopter and 8 Rappellers are assigned to the Daves Fire in California. Helibase duties, bucket work and line assignments for the crew are currently ongoing.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-06-15 14:48:04', 'After a short roll in R-5, the crew is en route to Utah. It&#039;s begun.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-06-17 10:18:30', 'Lyda and the rest of the gang are en route to Moab Utah to join up with the aircraft and crew on the Lackey Fan Fire. A 2 day drive should get the to the land of no shade.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-06-20 11:52:25', 'The crew has been reassigned to the Wild Rose fire in Rangely, CO. Pretty calm so far, but we remain vigilant while adapting to our new micro meteorological environment....');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-06-26 20:00:20', 'Time to get your cowboy on, the crew is now in Laramie, Wyoming for IA.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-06-30 21:19:40', 'Our thoughts and prayers go out to the friends and family of the Granite Mountain Hotshots as we anxiously await more news.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-07-03 14:37:28', 'The crew now has a Type 1 Sikorsky S-61 in our fleet that is currently helping out with all the lightning fires in the Vale, OR area. <br />\r\nThe rappel aircraft and crew are en route from Laramie, WY to enjoy all the blazing temps that Grants Pass has to offer. It&#039;s a dry heat.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-07-10 10:49:17', 'La Grande, Oregon calls so we answer. ');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-07-15 12:04:52', 'The crew is regrouping after a short stint in Northeast Oregon, and is now converging on the Mother Land that is Central Oregon. IA load is at the ready, while 8 are working hard to get a handle on the Buck Springs fire. <br />\r\nEvan and Nick are still rolling with the Type 1 even though it looks to be heading back to GP.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFires, rappels and predicted lightning are keeping us all busy.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-07-22 09:55:37', '19 rappellers are currently at Grants Pass enjoying the sunny, hot and dry weather.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-07-26 18:43:24', 'The crew and numerous ground and air resources are currently engaged in fighting fire on the Rogue River- Siskiyou NF. Weather, dry fuels and tough terrain are making us earn it.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nStay tuned....');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-08-03 16:26:09', 'The crew is scattered across the Willamette NF on multiple lightning fires. Jonah is on a TFLD assignment, Brett is managing our type 1, and 4 boosters are still on the road in R-1.<br />\r\nWe are rappelled out.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-08-03 16:26:10', 'The crew is scattered across the Willamette NF on multiple lightning fires. Jonah is on a TFLD assignment, Brett is managing our type 1, and 4 boosters are still on the road in R-1.<br />\r\nWe are rappelled out.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-08-09 19:18:27', 'The crew has been heavily engaged in IA on the Willamette, Umpqua and Rogue River-Siskiyou National Forests.<br />\r\nBrett and Sarah are tag teaming the Type 1 duties and Jonah has moved up to DIVS(t) on the Big Windy Fire.<br />\r\nThis is the 8th consecutive day that we have emptied the base, and there is more lightning happening right now on the forest.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAugust is so dirty.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-09-05 14:13:41', 'A few crew members are out on single resource assignments while the rest of the gang is awaiting an assignment from Grants Pass. Lightning is on the forest and we are ready, but only time will tell.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-09-13 18:42:26', 'Sunny hot and dry, fire season continues with one more round of emptying the base on the Siskiyou&#039;s.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-09-24 14:51:47', 'According to the USFS, the ODF and the weather outside....fire season is officially over in SW Oregon. Project work, base clean up, training and staying dry are now the focus.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-10-21 14:49:24', 'The temps are all off for the season and doing what they do in their natural environment, while the permanent staff holds down the fort and un-furloughs the base. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nCongratulations are also in order for our Rappeller of the Year, Richard Andrew Larrimore! Right on Larry.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-10-30 16:21:05', 'As things quiet down and the cooler weather starts to roll in, we turn our attention to hiring for the 2014 season. We look to make job offers the 2nd or 3rd week of January, so get your application in early and set up an appointment to come by the base while we&#039;re still around.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-11-18 10:01:33', 'If you are interested in applying to the crew for the 2014 field season, you have roughly 1 month to get your application in and stop by the base for a tour. Keep checking the recruiting tab often as this is also the time when the OCR numbers may change or be updated to replace the currently listed ones that show an end date of November 29, 2013.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nQuestions in text format? Call us.<br />\r\nVisual learner with questions? Stop by the base.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGood luck with your decision.<br />\r\n');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2013-12-16 12:55:47', 'The hiring process continues and we look to have the updated job announcements posted in USA Jobs after the first of the year for your reading enjoyment. If you have any questions, call or stop by the base. Otherwise keep an eye out for the updates on the web and the recruiting page of our website.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-01-06 13:35:04', 'Hiring Update:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs of this morning, we have requested an announcement number to be generated for the 2014 temp hiring and should be receiving it shortly. Once we have the number in hand we will post it in the recruiting section of our website and be making calls to those we have been in contact with. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nKeep an eye and ear out.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-01-08 17:10:28', 'The outreach for the PSE 13/13 GS-4/5 Senior Firefighter position is out and we should have it posted on USAJobs by the end of the week if all goes well. We are looking to potentially fill 2 positions on the crew and have already received good interest.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf you are interested in applying, come prepared and ready to work.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-01-18 10:37:12', 'The announcement numbers for our temporary GS-4/5 positions are now on USAJobs for your viewing and applying pleasure, and are also on our recruiting page. The announcements close January 23rd at midnight (EST), so hopefully you have all your documents ready to hit the send button. If you need assistance, give us a call and we will guide you down the path to the Siskiyou&#039;s!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGood luck.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-01-28 10:48:11', 'We are still waiting for Grants Pass to be added to the GS-5 Senior Firefighter position as a duty station and are hopeful that it will be completed this week. Keep an eye out and make sure your application is complete as we will be requesting a referral list approximately 10 days after it shows up on USAJobs.<br />\r\nThat is all.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-01-28 16:03:45', '**GS-4/5 Update**<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe announcement number for the permanent 13/13 GS-4/5 Senior Firefighter is now showing Grants Pass as a duty station in USAJobs. We will be requesting a referral list on Tuesday February 12th to continue the hiring process.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame time.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-02-21 14:32:38', 'We have made the decision to not have a rookie class for FY14 due to the limited amount of turnover we are experiencing. We do however encourage you to keep in touch throughout the field season if you are still interested in employment to keep your foot in the door for FY15.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe are also still awaiting our GS-4/5 Senior Firefighter list which should be here by the first part of next week. We hope.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-02-26 15:38:30', 'We have finally received the GS-4/5 Senior Firefighter list and are in the process of evaluating the applicants. We should have a decision to forward on to the Regional Office in the next 2-3 weeks.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-03-17 13:40:21', 'The selection for our GS-5 Senior Firefighter is at the Regional Office for final approval and we are looking to have a decision from them this week. ');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2014-03-27 16:28:39', 'Albuquerque is doing a final quals check on our GS-5 selection and has notified us that we should be able to make our job offer on Monday, March 31st.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-04-02 10:21:54', 'Congratulations to Andrew Larrimore on becoming our new GS-5 Senior Firefighter in our Operations Department. Andrew has worked hard to obtain his qualifications, has a great attitude and is dedicated to our program. Those qualities will take him far and we welcome him to the crew on a more permanent basis.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-04-08 10:12:01', 'With support from the Rogue River-Siskiyou N.F. the crew is expanding our permanent workforce. We have recently added an apprentice position on the crew and it has been filled with Jessica Crump from the Gold Beach Ranger District. Jessica has completed her hours as an apprentice and has been converted into this new developmental position on the crew as a GS-5 Senior Firefighter and will assist us with administrative duties as well as supporting all departments to round out her knowledge base. <br />\r\nHer strong work ethic, excellent physical fitness level and desire to learn have given her the foundation to succeed in this position and we welcome her to the crew.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-04-08 10:19:22', 'In the next 2 weeks we say goodbye to Sarah Uvodich and wish her well in her new position on the High Cascades Ranger District of the Rogue River-Siskiyou N.F. as their Prevention Technician. Sarah has been on the crew as our GS-5 Senior Firefighter in the Equipment Department for some time now and her knowledge, professionalism and dedication to the program will be missed. We know that she will do great in her new position and are glad that she will remain within reach on the forest.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis vacancy will also open up another opportunity for interested individuals in the coming months. We look to outreach for this opening this field season with an intent to fill this fall. Detail opportunities may also be available this season, so if you are interested give us a call.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-06-03 17:01:45', 'This past weekend we said farewell to our Fire Staff Kevin Donham and wished him well in his retirement. It was/is a big loss for the forest and the fire community, but we move on as fire season waits for no man.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSpeaking of fire season, it has been officially declared in SW Oregon as of yesterday and the wind and heat are backing that up. It looks to be another dry one, but we are ready with the helicopter on the pad and a bustle of activity in the background as we fine tune things.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSee you on the line. ');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-06-22 14:23:51', 'Some small ODF fires have kept us tuned up while Hsu and Hastings take on HMGB duties at the Bryant Fire. So far things have been extremely dry and quiet, which can only mean 2 things for the future.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n1. We will get fires<br />\r\n2. We will not get fires<br />\r\n<br />\r\n');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-06-30 14:50:57', 'A moment of silence for the Granite Mountain Hotshots to start the day off, followed by a briefing with lightning in the forecast and a noticeable increase in temperature made us take pause. Quality communication and info sharing is the focus today as we continue to prepare ourselves for the potential event. <br />\r\n<br />\r\n&acirc;€œEsse Quam Videri&acirc;€');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-07-09 09:44:05', 'It is so sunny, hot and dry that it has scared all the thunderstorms away. Single Resource assignments aside, all is quiet.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEnd of report.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2014-07-13 22:13:17', 'Shave that mohawk, Hastings!<br />\r\nIf you&#039;re trying to get ahold of Crump, Hesseling, Ormond or Hastings you might have to try back in two or three days.  We just dropped them off in the Willamette with fire underfoot and no maps.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-07-20 13:19:00', 'The crew has been very busy on the Willamette National Forest helping out with the Bingham Complex both at the helibase and on the line. Initial attack fires were plentiful but large fire support is now the mission with the Santiam Helibase supporting the Bingham, Lizard, Bridge 99, Bear Butte and Logging Unit fires. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nTrainees are all over the place.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-07-22 13:18:57', 'In the past 2 days at Santiam Helibase, we have had a moment of silence for TJ Marovich, Shane Allen and Jeff Heath who were all fatally injured doing a job we all love to do. We also had the privilege of hearing a first hand account of the Iron 44 helicopter crash from a helicopter crewmember who was at the helispot when the aircraft went down. With the anniversary of the Andy Palmer incident just days away, we have taken some time to reflect and prepare further to honor their memory and learn from our past. <br />\r\nWe have a long season ahead of us still, take care of each other and never forget.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2014-07-24 13:38:13', 'We&#039;ve moved to Oakridge and are currently staffing one fire on the Willamette with 4 hraps (Hastings, Crump, Favorite &amp; Ormond).  The aircraft is now quietly awaiting an order of boosters as the weather heats back up...');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2014-07-24 13:43:34', 'Six of our crewmembers have been positioned in Prineville on a boost to the Central Oregon Rappel Crew -  if you&#039;re looking for Sailer, Bobic, Johnson, Gladney, Olsen or Fabris you&#039;ll find them on the Deschutes National Forest...');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2014-07-31 12:01:46', 'We have now logged 22 rappel operations in the past two weeks.  Fire activity has been extremely high on the Rogue-Siskiyou National Forest with over 30 active fires being prioritized and staffed as firefighters become available.  Currently in the field: Mayfield, Holloway, Hastings, Crump, Johnson &amp; Fabris staffing the Wagner #1 Fire - Ormond &amp; Larrimore staffing #717 on Winburn Butte near Ashland - Quinones is ICT3 of the Camp Creek Complex - Gladney, Sailer, Bobic &amp; Olsen still assisting the Central Oregon Rappellers out of Prineville, OR.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-08-13 10:43:55', 'We have been staying ahead of the lightning with a robust rappeller recycling program, and with the recent weather we may even get a slight respite. 6 on the Umpqua, 4 on the Siskiyou&#039;s and 4 in the hole with just over 5,000 strikes in Oregon....we got this.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-08-18 15:22:20', 'Boosters to Central Oregon, Mayfield cruising around Siskiyou Mountains in a Type 3, 2.5 loads in the Sky Lakes Wilderness and 3 MRC boosters on the last load.......clock work.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-09-01 08:47:44', 'Most of the crew has returned from the #790 fire after some hard fought days and long nights and are now at Prospect Helibase supporting the effort. A lot of hard work and planning went in to that fire along with an extensive para-cargo ordering process to get the edges locked in. 4 rappellers remain on the line in ghost mode, doing whatever they can to assist further.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBoosters at Central are rumored to return soon, along with a few on well deserved R&amp;R.  With the Happy Camp Complex column in the background, we clean up our gear and realize it ain&#039;t over yet.<br />\r\n');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-09-17 04:52:45', 'We have finished up with the #790 Fire and have now moved on to the Onion Mountain Fire. Initial attack with rappellers was our first shot and with the foothold it has in very steep and rugged terrain, we are now assisting with personnel in Operations, at the Grants Helibase and in the field gathering intel. Boosters from all over are supporting us as well to ensure that we are ready for any additional IA that could arise. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nIt has been a long summer with tons of productive work to keep us occupied and further our skills.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOn a more personal note, Everett Hsu was brought into this world by his mother Mary and his father Evan on September 16, 2014 at 1902. We are extremely proud to have another member of the family and we all look forward to hanging out with him and teaching him bad habits when things slow down. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nCongratulations to Mary and Evan!');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-09-23 20:34:31', 'Our thoughts and prayers go out to Wally Ochoa, his family and the Winema Hotshots. Wally was struck by a snag and is in the hospital surrounded by his family and friends. <br />\r\nWe are confident that this will only be a speed bump for Wally and that he will be leading the saws up a knife ridge with a smile on his face real soon.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHere&#039;s to your speedy recovery Wall, the baddest Sawyer I ever met.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-11-21 15:15:22', 'The outreach for our vacant GS-4/5 Senior Firefighter is now on the street and available for viewing. Get your app ready and give a call if you have questions, the list will be requested on December 16th.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nhttps://fsoutreach.gdcii.com/Outreach<br />\r\n');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-11-21 15:56:49', 'Congratulations to the 2014 Siskiyou Rappel Crew Rappeller of the Year, Tanner Ormond! ');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2014-12-17 14:45:05', 'The referral list for the GS-4/5 Senior Firefighter position has been requested and we will be starting the hiring process soon.  Hopefully you have your app in and have contacted the base.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGood luck.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2015-01-06 15:49:16', 'Our temporary job announcements have opened up in USAJobs and are linked on our recruiting page for your clicking enjoyment. It is also not too late to drop by the base for a face to face and get a feel for things, so give us a call to schedule a time.<br />\r\nThe closing date is January 12th for both the GS-4 and GS-5 so get on it.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2015-01-21 10:26:19', 'We have received our GS-4/5 Senior Firefighter 13/13 list and are diligently working on it. Up to 4 candidates will be selected to be on the crew with start dates hopefully in the next few months. ');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2015-02-22 08:17:48', 'The selections have been made for our four GS-4/5 Senior Firefighter positions and have also been approved by our Forest Supervisor. Notifications should go out shortly from ASC with expected start dates of April 1st.<br />\r\nThis will conclude Phase 1 of our hiring plan and if all goes well, Phase 2 should take place in 2017 with the addition of 3 more Senior Firefighters on the roster.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTemporary hiring has been completed for the upcoming season, as well as our deadline for accepting detailers. The list is set and we will have 22 on the up list for whatever may come our way.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('tlyda', '2015-03-11 09:49:12', 'Just a quick update as time is getting closer to the 2015 Fire Season,  I want to Congratulate our new GS-5 Seniors, E.J. Brooks, Gregg Reidelbach, Justin Holloway and Charlie Fabris,  So all the hiring has been completed and we are 22 strong for this year .Thanks again to all that applied for the perm and temp jobs.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2015-06-12 07:27:44', 'Fire season is off to a running start!  Rookies have already logged 2 operational rappels and we&#039;ve staffed 5 fires, including ICT5, ICT4 and ICT3 incidents.  We are currently hosting 5 additional aircraft at our helibase and are providing logistical support for a number of fires in the area as well as covering initial attack with the help of the Malheur Rappel Crew and 0WW.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2015-06-20 08:21:09', 'The commotion from our last lightning bust has subsided and we&#039;ve begun sending some folks out on assignments to Alaska and the Buckskin Fire.  In preparation for the next round of lightning, we&#039;re researching mobile GIS technology and real-time location sharing to improve IA intel, raising our equipment stocking levels, and as always... training.  We&#039;re ready for a busy summer.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2015-07-04 13:44:43', 'Sunny, hot and dry on this 4th of July with BBQ and standby on the menu.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMerica!!');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('evanhsu', '2015-07-09 07:20:57', 'The past week has been busy for the crew, logging 6 fires in 7 days on 3 different forests.  We still have a handful of folks out on single resource assignments with 1 in Alaska as an EMT, 1 in Washington as an engine boss, 1 out as a crew boss, 2 managing our Sky Crane, and 1 as an ICT4 on the Buckskin fire.  More lightning is predicted this week as our firefighters trickle back to the base from their fires...');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2015-07-30 18:35:17', 'Fires to the South and columns in view from the base combined with a Haines 6 and 110 degree heat. It&#039;s coming.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2015-08-01 09:29:10', 'Rappellers on the Klamath NF and Brown Mountain, Wenatchee boosters leaking coconut oil on our flight steps and another boost order in the hopper. With the forecasted weather for today being LAL 6, 105 degrees and 10% RH, the guys in the field are struggling to keep their fires in check and we are supporting them from the base logistically.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe received word that there was a fatality on the Modoc on July 30th and our condolences go out to the family and friends of our fallen brother.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWork hard and take care of each other.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2015-08-01 18:50:17', 'Current Status:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n 4 rappellers on the Granite Fire on the Klamath NF, 4 on the Brown Mountain West Fire, 4 on the Strickland, 1 in Alaska with the Rogue River Hotshots, 1 on the Colville as ABRO(t), 1 in Spokane as ENGB(t), 1 on the Willamette as ASGS(t), boosters from John Day are en route and a Check Spotter is on order so Ballard can strut his stuff.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nOur Type 2 aircraft is supporting fires on the Siskiyou Mountains Ranger District and our Type 1 aircraft is on the Cable Crossing Fire.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nLightning is currently on the forest.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2015-08-03 09:13:06', 'We have rappelled out the last 3 days and today is not expected to be any different. 70 fires on the forest, Type 3 team in-briefing today and unstaffed fires on all districts. Additional booster orders are in and we are heading to the Gold Beach Ranger District this morning.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFirst Load!');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2015-08-06 14:38:11', 'Day 6 of no rappellers available with heavy IA on the forest and supporting existing fires logistically.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCongratulations go out to Brett Ballard for becoming our newest qualified Spotter. His first task after working so hard to attain his new qual? Give Tim Saturday off.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSpecial thanks to Mike Davis for taking the time to give Brett a look.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCasey Woodward is now in the hot seat with Mad Dog working towards his Spotter certification as well and lightning is in the forecast for tomorrow. Good luck Casey.');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2015-08-20 16:40:42', 'We have been assisting with the firefighting efforts, mainly in SW Oregon, for some time now. We have SRC personnel on the Collier Butte, Stouts, boosters in Central Oregon and a small contingent of IA rappellers at home. Both aircraft have been busy with all sorts of missions helping the forest hold on to what we have.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIt is a drastically different situation in some other areas however, with large fires pushing multiple GACC&#039;s to PL5 and creating surge forces due to critical resource shortages. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe join others in mourning the loss of 3 of our own and are thinking of those that are fighting the big ones.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAnd we still have potentially 2 more months of fire season still ahead of us.......');
INSERT INTO `current` VALUES('dquinones', '2015-09-14 13:55:49', 'The fires have come, have gone and have lingered depending on their location. The crew has been active, primarily in SW Oregon, for the last several weeks. The Collier Butte Fire and the National Creek Complex have been getting the majority of their attention with some rappel fires in between. Several crewmembers are out on single resource assignments to help the national effort and to advance their training.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThere has been some pretty exciting fire behavior on incidents within our region and now it appears that it is California&#039;s turn in the spot light. We stand behind all the firefighters actively engaged on these incidents and look forward to raising a glass with you here soon. <br />\r\n<br />\r\nFor now, think ahead, work hard and look out for each other.......Omnis Cedo Domus.');
